UX_COMPLETE
Agent: experience
Timestamp: 2026-06-19

## Conversion Flow Summary

Entry → PageHero (orientation) → ProductDetail left column (evaluate specs, select variant) →
ProductDetail right column sticky (InquiryForm always visible on desktop) →
Submit → InquirySuccess with WhatsApp escalation → Mister recovery CTA for non-converting buyers

## Top 3 Friction Points Resolved

1. TRUST AT WRONG MOMENT
   Was: "Consulta sin compromiso. Sin cuenta requerida." placed at top of form, before fields.
   Fixed: Moved trust signal to directly above submit button as "Respuesta en 24 horas · Sin compromiso de compra"
   (DM Mono 10px navy/50). Fogg's model: motivation must be highest at the moment of maximum resistance.

2. NO SAVED STATE — COMPARISON SHOPPING DESTROYS PROGRESS
   Was: Form fields reset on every page load. B2B buyers who navigate away mid-form lose all progress.
   Fixed: Debounced localStorage save (800ms) on every field change to `wings_inquiry_${product.slug}`.
   Restored on mount. Cleared after successful submit or after 7-day expiry. Full SSR-safe try/catch.

3. NO COMPLETION CEREMONY — SILENT SUBMIT BUTTON
   Was: Submit button identical whether form is empty or fully valid. No visible finish line.
   Fixed: SVG rect border overlaid on button animates pathLength 0→1 in gold (#C4933F) over 600ms
   when all required fields simultaneously valid. On successful submit: stamp animation (scale 1→0.96→1,
   rotate 0→-1→0, 400ms). Both skip on prefers-reduced-motion. Goal Gradient: visible finish line
   accelerates completion in the final stage.

## Additional Enhancements Implemented

- Auto-focus on full_name field on desktop (non-mobile) on form load
- Goal Gradient field pulse: on valid field blur, next field wrapper receives gold box-shadow pulse
  (200ms, rgba(196,147,63,0.5)) drawing the eye forward through the sequence
- Select (país de destino) triggers quantity pulse on value change — closes the blur-event gap for selects
- Removed redundant top-of-form trust signal (was duplicating signal at wrong position)
- Preserved all existing functionality: variant badge, product ref field, error states, toast on failure

